    slug_id: 'web-performance-optimization',
    slug_en: 'web-performance-optimization',
    title: 'Web Performance Optimization Tips',
    excerpt_id: 'Tips untuk membuat website lebih cepat dan improve user experience.',
    excerpt_en: 'Learn how to make your website faster and improve user experience.',
    body_id: `## Ringkasan

Web performance直接影响 user experience, conversion rates, dan SEO rankings. Panduan ini mencakup practical tips untuk optimize website speed dan performance.

## Key Points

- Page speed直接影响 conversion rates (1s delay = 7% reduction)
- Core Web Vitals adalah ranking factor Google
- Image optimization memberikan impact terbesar
- JavaScript optimization critical untuk performance
- Caching strategies essential untuk repeat visitors
- CDN usage improves global performance
- Performance optimization adalah continuous process

## Core Web Vitals

### Largest Contentful Paint (LCP)
Target: < 2.5 seconds
Measures loading performance.

### First Input Delay (FID)
Target: < 100 milliseconds
Measures interactivity.

### Cumulative Layout Shift (CLS)
Target: < 0.1
Measures visual stability.

## Image Optimization

### Techniques
- Use WebP format (25-35% smaller than JPEG)
- Implement lazy loading
- Responsive images dengan srcset
- Proper sizing (don't serve 2000px images untuk 400px containers)
- Compression tools: TinyPNG, ImageOptim

### Best Practices
- Use CDN untuk image delivery
- Implement progressive loading
- Remove unnecessary metadata
- Use SVG untuk icons dan logos

## JavaScript Optimization

### Strategies
- Minimize JavaScript payload
- Code splitting untuk large applications
- Tree shaking untuk remove unused code
- Defer non-critical JavaScript
- Use async untuk independent scripts

### Tools
- Webpack Bundle Analyzer
- Rollup untuk libraries
- Terser untuk minification

## CSS Optimization

### Techniques
- Remove unused CSS
- Minify CSS files
- Critical CSS inline
- Non-critical CSS async loading
- Use CSS containment

## Caching Strategies

### Browser Caching
- Set appropriate Cache-Control headers
- Leverage ETags untuk validation
- Service workers untuk offline caching
- Long cache times untuk static assets (1 year)

### Server-Side Caching
- Object caching (Redis, Memcached)
- Page caching untuk static content
- Database query caching
- CDN edge caching

## Content Delivery Network (CDN)

### Benefits
- Reduced latency untuk global users
- Offload traffic dari origin server
- DDoS protection
- Automatic compression

### Providers
- Cloudflare (free tier available)
- AWS CloudFront
- Fastly
- BunnyCDN

## Server Optimization

### Backend Improvements
- Use latest PHP/Node.js/Rust versions
- Enable HTTP/2 atau HTTP/3
- Gzip/Brotli compression
- Database optimization
- Use faster web servers (Nginx)

### Hosting Considerations
- SSD storage mandatory
- Adequate RAM
- Geographic proximity to users
- Scalability options

## Performance Monitoring

### Tools
- Google PageSpeed Insights
- GTmetrix
- WebPageTest
- Lighthouse
- Chrome DevTools Performance tab

### Metrics to Track
- Time to First Byte (TTFB)
- First Contentful Paint (FCP)
- Time to Interactive (TTI)
- Total page size
- Number of requests

## Mobile Performance

### Special Considerations
- Test on 3G/4G networks
- Reduce mobile payload
- Touch optimization
- Viewport configuration
- Avoid heavy animations

## Conclusion

Performance optimization требует continuous effort. Start dengan quick wins (images, caching), then tackle more complex optimizations.

**Priority actions:**
1. Run performance audit
2. Optimize images
3. Implement caching
4. Setup CDN
5. Monitor continuously`,
